@FunctionalInterface public static non-sealed interface EventQueryRowHandler.AsMap extends EventQueryRowHandler, Consumer<Map<String,?>>
FunctionalInterface to be implemented for consuming query result rows as JSON maps. This can be used for queries similar to FROM e IN events ... PROJECT INTO { id: e.id, ... }.
